        <num>CC 2910</num>
        <heading>2910.  Substance and place of performance</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2910.  Substance and place of performance
The borrower is bound to render performance at the place agreed upon.  When the place for performance is not fixed in the contract, performance shall be rendered at the place where the loan is contracted.</p>
        </content>
